{"tid":529594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國藥局研究；成熟男人只在意女性樣貌， 不在意身材","createTime":"2018-01-15T02:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T03:06:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":32,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c03d2da4c2ae3e8e415758023988e00a86f3b40d","tid":529594,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.nmplus.hk/social-buzz/身材-研究-男女/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2Fsocial-buzz%2F%E8%BA%AB%E6%9D%90-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%2F&d=yp0hCdc8ZBVYQO1P1IY3D8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=21eeed4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nmplus.hk/social-buzz/身材-研究-男女/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n淨係睇身材代表你幼稚！ 英國研究：「成熟男人只會睇樣」<br />\nSOCIAL BUZZ<br />\non January 11, 2018 at 22:45<br />\n<br />\n經常有人話男人只懂用「下面諗嘢」，看女人只看身材。但最近英國藥局則出了一份研究，要大家知不要「一竹篙打一船人」，研究顯示不同年齡層對異性的審美觀存在分別。首先比較吸引年青男性的是對方身材，而隨著年齡增長，男性漸漸傾向只在意女性的樣貌&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n男性審美觀隨年齡變化 只看身材代表你幼稚！<br />\n<br />\n英國藥局的「菲力克斯博士」（Dr. Felix）發表了研究，指出人的審美觀除了男女有別之外，男性方面更會隨著年齡變化，改變其審美觀。18至34歲組別的年輕男性，異性的身材會較樣貌更吸引，身材愈火辣則會較受到歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n這個現象隨年齡增加，出現變化，男人會漸漸變得重視對方的樣貌多於身材，直到65歲，樣貌成為了最吸引人的地方。但以整體所有年齡層來說，樣子才是男性的主要審美標準，近有46％的參與者認為樣子才最重要。其次就是屁股，有18％的人喜歡屁股翹翹的女性；11％喜歡髮型，而只有9％以及1％喜歡腿部和眼睛。<br />\n<br />\n男性胸肌最吸引女性<br />\n<br />\n女性方面的表現就比較上平均，各個年齡層也有不同的審美觀，最吸引到女性的首先是男性的胸膛，佔24％；22％參與者喜歡髮型；19％及13％喜歡強壯的手臂以及腹肌，9％的女性喜歡男性的人魚線，但只有2％的女性重視男性的樣貌。而18- 24歲年輕女性較喜歡的部份跟男性相同，也就是對方各方面的身材。25至34歲則比較重視臉部，對健壯身型的喜好也漸漸下降，但注意的是胸膛部份一直都是最吸引所有女性的部份，直到65歲的女性比較著重對方的頭髮。因為男性到了這個年齡層，都可能會有禿頭的問題，所以若然有一頭秀髮的話，也已經是十分吸引。"},{"pid":"aab1fdebbf493755f63b04a73b580fe67b077987","tid":529594,"uid":49197,"like":99,"dislike":3,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"屌終於還我清白<br />\n我不嬲睇女係睇樣重要好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5a135b557720c896943f625ee6656cabdb9d92","tid":529594,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"ddd7ed35a0850f8611572482d349454bf9c0b8ae","tid":529594,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":66,"score":-64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"樣靚身材一定唔差<br />\n樣靚可以肥，但一定唔會好肥。"},{"pid":"1405af64068cb294bb78f8e12330e94664ca1f99","tid":529594,"uid":134071,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"ddd7ed35a0850f8611572482d349454bf9c0b8ae","tid":529594,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":66,"score":-64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"樣靚身材一定唔差<br />\n樣靚可以肥，但一定唔會好肥。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"有唔少人樣靚但波細"},{"pid":"07ba61f68f0f7c5a6258382c672d785697cdee0d","tid":529594,"uid":39439,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"唔怪得我見到靚仔會扯旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb6a6e844bad2e250fb4e273f60714967dc8a0e","tid":529594,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1405af64068cb294bb78f8e12330e94664ca1f99","tid":529594,"uid":134071,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"ddd7ed35a0850f8611572482d349454bf9c0b8ae","tid":529594,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":66,"score":-64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"樣靚身材一定唔差<br />\n樣靚可以肥，但一定唔會好肥。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"有唔少人樣靚但波細"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"總比無樣又無波好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c44e5f61d4d5968463570f3cfc09f7477eb9911","tid":529594,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1405af64068cb294bb78f8e12330e94664ca1f99","tid":529594,"uid":134071,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"ddd7ed35a0850f8611572482d349454bf9c0b8ae","tid":529594,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":66,"score":-64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"樣靚身材一定唔差<br />\n樣靚可以肥，但一定唔會好肥。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"有唔少人樣靚但波細"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"細極都有個輪廓呱"},{"pid":"b2553aff75e421aa28394cda96101dd9259ad7e1","tid":529594,"uid":38793,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">英國研究</span>"},{"pid":"3af76ab8aab818ab63db8f6cf1993de2d9a53173","tid":529594,"uid":52194,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"樣波蘿腿<br />\n魚與熊掌不能兼得<br />\n有兩樣中就狗衝啦<br />\n中哂四樣嘅只有人造人"},{"pid":"5d9337ad72a199912a326eef2dcfd71b51c35a07","tid":529594,"uid":52194,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣<br />\n處<br />\n過左十六歲產量少一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244110adebaabb9a196ce3371b9a0fc90f0535b5","tid":529594,"uid":17628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"個研究係咪港女in charge <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff51fb470c058c798ef51161f4b6e9a26fcbee27","tid":529594,"uid":42283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:16:46.000Z","msg":"咁成熟男人個個都接受到男人至啱<br />\n反正平到AAA都唔重要"},{"pid":"34d135e4e451db46b344e08e6495ab951dce9541","tid":529594,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d9337ad72a199912a326eef2dcfd71b51c35a07","tid":529594,"uid":52194,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣<br />\n處<br />\n過左十六歲產量少一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"十四歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b53faa21722a87ce56cb4d12fca677d7254ddcd","tid":529594,"uid":139965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"英國研究都算 關藥局咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6fa70d4ab1ec9